---
title: Sauteed Garlic Broccolini & Green Beans with Lemon, Mint & Feta | Serves 2
description: This abundant bowl of green goodness is sure to put the pep in your step! With lemon, chilli and mint, there's plenty of zest and a gentle kick of heat, while feta adds a delicious creamy touch.
